{"tid":433433,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[貓咪音樂台]港貓唔可以俾蝗族欺負《港貓爭氣》MV","createTime":"2017-10-12T11:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T17:31:57.000Z","uid":50360,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"40c10f8e853220d4b9fe007808ba08ffbeba66f4","tid":433433,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T11:20:59.000Z","msg":"即係咁，一個大陸人好屈唔屈去屈一隻貓，仲要搞到貓貓病埋。作為一個貓奴，好難唔出聲，亦好難唔搵人唱爆佢。如果貓店長波子真係抓傷大陸婦人個仔，道歉露出XX是常識吧﹗但依家老屈隻貓抓傷人，仲要搞大件事Call漁農處捉貓，真係當香港人同港貓好蝦？冇野嘛？﹗依家全港貓奴都撐波子呀﹗仲有，什麼「保外就醫」，依家影片證明波子冇抓人，係咪要反告大陸婦浪費警力同虛假報案，仲要佢賠償波子嘅醫藥費同心靈損失？<br />\n<br />\n貓係可愛呀，但唔代表可以任人摸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《港貓爭氣》MV：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JdkUFpAllKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJdkUFpAllKs&d=l0vifx8IMaGqayQhSVpMogdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=7146dada\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JdkUFpAllKs</a>"},{"pid":"553580a1eee2f90d62a881d81f90ab82ec9a70e3","tid":433433,"uid":50360,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"《港貓爭氣》<br />\n<br />\n原曲：爭氣<br />\n改編填詞：山卡啦<br />\n主唱：若智子<br />\nMV製作：山卡啦<br />\n<br />\n蝗媽  藥房內嘈嚷生事聲稱  貓碰人<br />\n還撒野  報定案又要搞大這事  才甘心<br />\n極度低等  告店長波子傷害抓出  一血痕<br />\n片段重溫  即使無實證  但上身<br />\n<br />\n又說謊  愛做戲  害到波子在逃避<br />\n預約好  要把波子監裡去  就等死<br />\n無實證  才卑鄙  這政府  偏受理<br />\n換來  誣蔑惡行錯得起<br />\n<br />\n被你撫摸已揈尾  直接出爪是權利<br />\n做店長  也不等於給你戲弄和扯尾<br />\n誰亦會谷氣  蝗族橫蠻無道理<br />\n害人  拿波子出來受氣<br />\n<br />\n極度黑心  說阿仔給貓抓後傷痛  已嚇親<br />\n北方到港賤人  橫蠻無理  沒法忍<br />\n<br />\n又說謊  愛做戲  害到波子在逃避<br />\n預約好  要把波子監裡去  就等死<br />\n無實證  才卑鄙  這政府  偏受理<br />\n為何  蝗族惡行給包庇<br />\n<br />\n唐貓  波子必要爭氣  無理被老屈痛悲<br />\n判坐監  為求大媽歡喜  全力對抗為港貓打氣<br />\n<br />\n又說謊  愛做戲  害到波子在逃避<br />\n預約好  要把波子監裡去  就等死<br />\n無實證  才卑鄙  這政府  偏受理<br />\n換來  誣蔑惡行錯得起<br />\n<br />\n就算貓咪有耐性  但會出爪在防備<br />\n做店長  有班街坊喜愛與及來打氣<br />\n誣陷太激氣  明明大話還做戲<br />\n賤人  拿波子出來受氣"},{"pid":"fdbb3ea307535e259c6d903377ba940900c2063c","tid":433433,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T11:56:42.000Z","msg":"蝗族屈喵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4901f57641be4c5f40ac684f266e964ffc9cf79","tid":433433,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:12:27.000Z","msg":"蝗族屈喵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a768a87feb29d8cea9d4424fdaff37f5a81f19","tid":433433,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f34611e5475e2ea3bc38f3fefbd2de27a91f920","tid":433433,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:35:06.000Z","msg":"蝗族屈喵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23095b836101bfaaeeb0e14cc59f5a478189e93e","tid":433433,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:10:28.000Z","msg":"蝗族屈喵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95121549e996d3a50823641d11dba39307e34668","tid":433433,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"正喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f936652da0af442f98e5a889be46373cca345aa2","tid":433433,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:47:00.000Z","msg":"北方到港賤人 橫蠻無理 沒法忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgm